and half the cost to operate,

373
00:40:27,945 --> 00:40:30,861
would your bank invest
in a thousand of them?

374
00:40:34,952 --> 00:40:36,649
Have you built such a tractor?

375
00:41:24,784 --> 00:41:27,831
To the future
of the Lamborghini tractor.

376
00:41:27,874 --> 00:41:30,137
- We did it.
- We did it.

377
00:41:37,362 --> 00:41:39,103
She should be here with us.

378
00:41:40,626 --> 00:41:43,368
- To Clelia.
- To Clelia.

379
00:41:47,677 --> 00:41:48,678
Look who's here.

380
00:41:54,945 --> 00:41:58,557
I'm crazy about her, Ferruccio.

381
00:41:58,601 --> 00:42:01,429
I see her face
when I close my eyes to sleep,

382
00:42:01,473 --> 00:42:03,649
and it's there
when I open them to wake.

383
00:42:04,476 --> 00:42:05,999
You're in love.

384
00:42:06,043 --> 00:42:07,740
I'm in love.

385
00:42:07,784 --> 00:42:12,179
Go get her.
Tomorrow it may be too late.

386
00:42:19,404 --> 00:42:20,492
I have to go.

387
00:42:21,319 --> 00:42:24,191
Go? Where are you going?

388
00:42:24,235 --> 00:42:25,366
I'm sorry.

389
00:42:27,717 --> 00:42:30,241
- Talk to her.
- Yeah.

390
00:43:02,926 --> 00:43:04,710
Did my friend talk to you?

391
00:43:04,754 --> 00:43:05,798
He did.

392
00:43:06,886 --> 00:43:08,583
He doesn't catch my eye.

393
00:43:09,715 --> 00:43:10,847
You do.

394
00:43:11,674 --> 00:43:12,936
But you know that.

395
00:43:12,979 --> 00:43:15,329
Give him a chance.

396
00:43:15,373 --> 00:43:17,070
Why should I do that?

397
00:43:18,463 --> 00:43:20,378
Because he deserves one.

398
00:43:20,421 --> 00:43:21,945
So do I.

399
00:43:27,907 --> 00:43:29,300
My wife died.

400
00:43:30,257 --> 00:43:33,521
I know. What was her name?

401
00:43:34,435 --> 00:43:35,698
Clelia.

402
00:43:36,916 --> 00:43:38,004
She was beautiful.

403
00:43:38,048 --> 00:43:39,919
She was everything.

404
00:43:42,530 --> 00:43:44,010
Don't sit.

405
00:43:44,054 --> 00:43:47,231
If you do, I will let you.

406
00:43:49,799 --> 00:43:53,237
I'll only take
what you have to give me
because I need it.

407
00:43:55,282 --> 00:43:57,502
And some day
you will hate me for it.

408
00:43:58,982 --> 00:43:59,896
No.

409
00:44:02,855 --> 00:44:05,858
I won't. Never.

410
00:44:40,414 --> 00:44:42,199
You just want more.

411
00:44:43,287 --> 00:44:45,680
You always want more.

412
00:44:45,724 --> 00:44:47,508
You want me to say I'm sorry?

413
00:44:47,552 --> 00:44:49,684
I'm sorry.

414
00:44:49,728 --> 00:44:52,035
Where is your shame, Ferruccio?

415
00:44:55,865 --> 00:44:57,692
I wanted to say it's Clelia,

416
00:44:57,736 --> 00:44:59,564
that her death has changed you,

417
00:44:59,607 --> 00:45:02,262
but in my heart
I know that is not true.

418
00:45:02,306 --> 00:45:05,004
This is who you are.
Who you've always been.

419
00:45:05,048 --> 00:45:06,832
Tonino needs a mother.

420
00:45:06,876 --> 00:45:08,747
So, yes,
I took her because I could.

421
00:45:08,791 --> 00:45:11,184
Think about what I just said
Matteo, because I could.

422
00:45:11,228 --> 00:45:13,447
If I didn't take her,
someone else would have.

423
00:45:13,491 --> 00:45:16,711
I'm sorry, but she was never
going to be yours.

424
00:45:16,755 --> 00:45:20,150
How can I hurt my friend
by taking something
that he never had?

425
00:45:24,371 --> 00:45:26,069
Don't let this change things,
Matteo.

426
00:45:29,507 --> 00:45:30,508
I need you.

427
00:45:31,639 --> 00:45:33,641
I've always needed you.

428
00:45:33,685 --> 00:45:35,513
Clelia knew that.

429
00:45:35,556 --> 00:45:37,558
Clelia was the smart one.

430
00:45:39,386 --> 00:45:42,302
She said nothing good
could come of this,

431
00:45:43,129 --> 00:45:44,609
and look what happened.

432
00:45:50,093 --> 00:45:52,965
I want 25 percent
of the company.

433
00:45:54,749 --> 00:45:56,316
The rest is yours.

434
00:46:30,829 --> 00:46:32,178
<i>Tre mignon.</i>

435
00:46:39,185 --> 00:46:40,360
<i>Due cornetti.</i>

436
00:46:42,449 --> 00:46:45,409
One Sacher torte,
in its own box.

437
00:46:47,672 --> 00:46:49,152
Thank you.

438
00:47:03,209 --> 00:47:04,123
Ciao Bella.

439
00:47:17,658 --> 00:47:20,139
- Is Annita in the office?
- She is.

440
00:47:21,575 --> 00:47:23,186
- Red or blue?
- Red.

441
00:47:23,229 --> 00:47:27,407
- Not blue?
- Definitely red.
Definitely red.

442
00:47:27,451 --> 00:47:29,105
Who screwed up?

443
00:47:29,148 --> 00:47:31,237
It wasn't us.

444
00:47:31,281 --> 00:47:32,978
Ferruccio!

445
00:47:37,113 --> 00:47:38,549
Go see what she wants.

446
00:47:38,592 --> 00:47:39,724
Not me.

447
00:47:39,767 --> 00:47:40,986
You're a coward.

448
00:47:50,648 --> 00:47:52,345
You look beautiful this morning.

449
00:47:52,389 --> 00:47:54,478
I'm sorry I had to leave early.

450
00:47:54,521 --> 00:47:57,002
Did I mention you
look beautiful this morning?

451
00:48:00,049 --> 00:48:03,574
Every time you buy pastries
it costs us money.

452
00:48:03,617 --> 00:48:05,097
Well, take it from my salary.

453
00:48:05,141 --> 00:48:07,491
You forget, I own the company.

454
00:48:07,534 --> 00:48:08,709
Is that so?

455
00:48:09,797 --> 00:48:12,148
Mrs. Giambini called.

456
00:48:12,191 --> 00:48:14,541
Who's-who's Giambini?

457
00:48:14,585 --> 00:48:15,978
She isn't happy
with her tractor?

458
00:48:16,021 --> 00:48:18,893
No, she is unhappy with Tonino.

459
00:48:18,937 --> 00:48:21,070
She's his teacher.

460
00:48:21,113 --> 00:48:23,463
Tesoro, you have to spend
more time with him.

461
00:48:23,507 --> 00:48:24,856
I give him everything.

462
00:48:24,899 --> 00:48:27,598
Yes, you give him money,
clothes, cars.

463
00:48:27,641 --> 00:48:29,643
But of yourself?

464
00:48:29,687 --> 00:48:32,516
That's what he really wants.

465
00:48:32,559 --> 00:48:35,519
You know he is as smart
as you are, but he's failing.

466
00:48:35,562 --> 00:48:37,782
I'll talk to him.

467
00:48:37,825 --> 00:48:40,611
