has a new exhibit.

468
00:48:40,654 --> 00:48:43,483
- I hate your friend Diego.

469
00:48:43,527 --> 00:48:45,572
We should go, bring Tonino.

470
00:48:45,616 --> 00:48:48,010
Spend some time together
as a family.

471
00:48:58,020 --> 00:49:00,326
Goddamn clutch!

472
00:49:00,370 --> 00:49:03,416
Tonino, it never works.

473
00:49:08,160 --> 00:49:09,509
What do you think?

474
00:49:09,553 --> 00:49:10,858
About what?

475
00:49:11,859 --> 00:49:12,730
The boat.

476
00:49:12,773 --> 00:49:14,949
It's a present for you.

477
00:49:14,993 --> 00:49:17,126
Because I failed
all my subjects?

478
00:49:18,257 --> 00:49:20,172
- Yes.
- What happens next?

479
00:49:20,216 --> 00:49:23,219
We get in the boat,
you take me out to sea,
and throw me overboard?

480
00:49:26,135 --> 00:49:28,180
Come. Sit.

481
00:49:29,834 --> 00:49:30,704
Sit.

482
00:49:37,146 --> 00:49:39,539
Tonino, life is short.

483
00:49:39,583 --> 00:49:43,065
When one is young,
when one is beautiful,
like yourself,

484
00:49:44,414 --> 00:49:46,068
